    "body" : "Hey, FYI if you can want to replace simultaneous muti-linebreaks with single line break then you can use   <code>myString.trim().replaceAll(&quot;[\\n]{2,}&quot;, &quot;\\n&quot;)</code>  Or replace with a single space    <code>myString.trim().replaceAll(&quot;[\\n]{2,}&quot;, &quot; &quot;)</code>"
  } ],
