    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Linebreaks are not the same under windows/linux/mac. You should use <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.5.0/docs/api/java/lang/System.html#getProperties()\" rel=\"noreferrer\">System.getProperties</a> with the attribute line.separator.</p>\n"
