      "body" : "@Parthan_akon It&#39;s a regex. | means or. It will replace the first block that matches. So if there is \\r\\n, it will be replaced with one space. If there is a \\r but no \\n or the other way around, it will also be one space. He does it this way to prevent replacing \\r and \\n by a space and ending up with 2 spaces."
