    "creation_date" : 1493419112,
    "answer_id" : 43689791,
    "question_id" : 2163045,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><a href=\"https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-lang/apidocs/org/apache/commons/lang3/StringUtils.html#normalizeSpace-java.lang.String-\" rel=\"noreferrer\">This function</a> normalizes down all whitespace, including line breaks, to single spaces.  Not exactly what the original question asked for, but likely to do exactly what is needed in many cases:</p>\n\n<pre><code>import org.apache.commons.lang3.StringUtils;\n\nfinal String cleansedString = StringUtils.normalizeSpace(rawString);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
